          <dd>[Galleria Casa Serodine, Ascona, Switzerland], (1966), sold; to the Alice Corinne McDaniel Collection, Department of the Classics, Harvard University (1966-2012), transfer; to the Harvard Art Museums, 2012.</dd>
        
        
        
